Package: poly-c60-profile-kiosk
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: OpenPolycom <apt@openpolycom.cc>
Installed-Size: 7
Depends: cage, cog
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Description: C60 device profile: fullscreen web kiosk
 Metapackage selecting the web-kiosk role for the Polycom Trio C60: the
 same cage+cog Wayland kiosk as the TC8, on the C60's 720x1280 portrait
 panel. Pins the stack the base image ships; profile composition lives in
 the package archive (polycom_dev/PROFILES-PLAN.md).
